Landing.HeroSubHeading.SubHeadingHero: Pangani, yesani, ndi kufufuza zitsanzo, njira, ndi mphamvu. Fufuzani Cell Collective kwa:
Landing.HeroDescription.HeroDescriptionL: Phunzirani biology ndi biochemistry mwa kumanga ndi kupanga zitsanzo.
Landing.HeroDescription.HeroDescriptionR: Pezani kafukufuku pa malo akuluakulu okhudza zachilengedwe.
Landing.SubHero.FeatureRichDescription: Gulu la Network, Analysis ndi Visualization zonse, mu bokosi limodzi.
Landing.ColumnBanner.BuildModelsDescript: Tsatirani mitundu yambiri ya zinthu zamoyo, kuphatikizapo magetsi, ma genetic, mawotchi, mawonekedwe a maselo, maselo a zakudya, etc. zokhudzana ndi zamoyo zosiyanasiyana kuchokera ku mabakiteriya kupita ku mavairasi kupita ntchentche kupita kwa anthu. Fotokozani zitsanzo popanda kufunika kapena kusintha kusintha kovuta kwa masamu.
Landing.ColumnBanner.PerformStimulations: Gwiritsani ntchito nthawi yeniyeni, yogwirizana mofanana kuti muwonetsetse momwe zinthu zamoyo zimakhudzira zochitika zosiyanasiyana zowonjezereka komanso zowonongeka (monga, matenda). Kuthamangitsani zitsanzo zamakono zoyimirirako mu mphindi zochepa ndikupanga kusanthula-kutulutsira zowonongeka kuti muwone momwe mayankho a ma cellular alili pansi pazosiyana
Landing.ColumnBanner.AnalyzeResultsDescr: Fufuzani machitidwe ndi mayankho a machitidwe a zamoyo pansi pazikhalidwe zosiyanasiyana. Kuthamanga kafukufuku wotsutsana ndi machitidwe kuti athe kufotokozera ndi kulongosola zotsatira za munthu aliyense ndi kuphatikiza zigawo zikuluzikulu pa dongosolo. Lembani ndi kufufuza njira zokhudzana ndi mankhwala ndi zofunikira zothandizira.
Landing.VideoBanner.VideoBannerDescripti: Ophunzira safunikanso kuloweza mutu wa chilengedwe - akhoza kutsanzira ndikuwongolera njira zogwirira ntchito m'malo mogwiritsa ntchito mapulogalamu a Cell Collective modeling.
Landing.VideoBanner.VideoBannerStudentMe: <em> Ndapeza kuti pochita izi, ndimamvetsa mfundo zambiri pambuyo pake. </ em>
Landing.VideoBanner.VideoBannerStudentTi: Wophunzira wa Sayansi ya Zamoyo, <em> University of Nebraska-Lincoln </ em>
LandingPage.UniversityBanner.UniversityB: Kuchokera kwa ofufuza, kupita ku mayunivesite apamwamba padziko lonse
A 1000, ofunikira, aphunzitsi ndi ophunzira padziko lonse amagwiritsa ntchito Cell Collective kuti aphunzire, kumanga ndi kuyerekezera zitsanzo zachilengedwe.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase1.ClickOn: Dinani pa {photo} chithunzi kuti mupange chitsanzo chatsopano
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase1.Publish:
• KULULULIDWA MODELS ndizowonetseratu zochitika za anzanu, zofalitsidwa zomwe zinaperekedwa kwa gulu la Cell Collective kuti zikhale zofanana ndi zopereka zina.
  • ZITSANZO ZANGA muli zitsanzo zomwe munapanga ndi zanu.
  • KUKHALA NDI ME ndizojambulidwa zomwe ena amagwiritsa ntchito nanu. Gwiritsani ntchito pulojekitiyi kuti mumvetse bwino zitsanzo ndi othandizira anu popanda kutumiza mafayilo a SBML mobwerezabwereza.
  • Mpukutu Womanja kuti uone Mafano ena!
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase1.YouMayC: Mungasindikize chizindikiro {photo} nthawi iliyonse kuti mudziwe zambiri za Cell Collective.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ClickO: Dinani pa chithunzi kuti mutembenuke pakati pa {photo1} (Onani Njira) ndi {photo2} (Kusintha Mode). <ol> <li> Kawiri Dinani pa malo opanda kanthu kuti muwonjezere chigawo chatsopano. </ li> <li> Double Dinani Pezani kuti mutchulidwe kachigawo. </ li> <li> Shift + Dinani pang'onopang'ono kuti muzisinthe pakati Zosakaniza zakunja. </ li> <li> Sinthani pakati pa chithunzi cholakwika kapena chosayenerera ndi Shift + pang'onopang'ono pogwiritsa ntchito mzere wolumikiza. </ li> </ ol>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.NewMod: Zachigawo zatsopano zowonjezera zingaperekedwenso powonekera pano pa {photo}. Dinani kawiri chizindikiro kuti musinthe dzina lachinthu.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ToAddA: <span> Kuti muwonjezere munthu wotsegula kapena inhibitor, gwedeza ndi kusiya zigawozo kuchokera mndandanda wa Internal Components kapena Zomwe Zingokhala kunja ku bokosi lofotokozera la Drop Component. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.U: <span> Gwiritsani ntchito pulojekiti yosavuta kuti mupange zinthu zakunja (mwachitsanzo, zolemba zofanana). Mipata ingakhalenso yosiyanasiyana panthawi yomwe mukuyimira kuti muwonetsere kusintha kwa machitidwe a nthawi yeniyeni. Izi ndi zofanana ndi zosiyana siyana za chilengedwe ndi kuyang'ana zomwe zimayankha. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.S: Sankhani bokosi loyang'ana pansi pa chithunzi {photo} cha zigawo zomwe mukufuna kuziwona pa Girasi loyimira. Kuwongolera pa liwu lachigawo lidzawonetsa njira yake, kukulolani kuti mupeze mwatsatanetsatane chigawocho mkati mwa galasi lotanganidwa!
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.C: Dinani chizindikiro cha {photo1} kuti muyambe kuyerekezera. Mukhozanso kusinthana {photo2} kuti muime nthawi yomwe mukuyimira kapena muyambe kusinthasintha podalira chizindikiro cha {photo3}.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Dinani pa {photo} chithunzi kuti mupange kuyesedwa kwatsopano. Zofufuza zimatchulidwa mwachindunji mwa kuwonekera pa chizindikiro.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Use: <span> Gwiritsani ntchito pulojekiti yosavuta kuti mupange zochitika zakunja (mwachitsanzo, zopangira zofanana) kuti muyesere. Izi zikufanana ndi kukhazikitsa zizindikiro zakunja zokhudzana ndi zamoyo zomwe zikuchitika m'deralo, zomwe zimakhudza zomwe zimachitika. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Dinani pa {photo} iicon kuti muyambe kuyerekezera.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Dos: <span> Zithunzi za mayankho zimatha kupangidwira pazomwe zili muchitsanzo mwa kusankha gawo loyenera la X ndi Y-axis. Kawirikawiri, chigawo chapadera chimayimilira pa X-axis (pendent variable) pamene ziwalo za mkati zimayimilira pa Y-axis (zosiyana siyana). Mayendedwe angapo a mayendedwe amtundu angapangidwe kuchokera kuyesa limodzi. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouMayS: <span> Mungathe kufufuza zitsanzo mwa mutu, ndondomeko, ma tags kapena dzina la mapuloteni. Funso limodzi lingathe kufufuza Zithunzi Zosindikizidwa, Zanga Zanga, ndi Kugawana ndi Ine Makalata nthawi zonse. </ Span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.ChangeB: Sintha pakati pa Mndandanda ndi Grid View
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouCanC: <span> Mungasinthe malingaliro anu pakati pa mndandanda wawonekedwe ndi grid. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.InThisM: <span> Mu menyu awa mukhoza kusintha malonda anu, kusintha mawu anu achinsinsi, ndi kulowa. </ span>
JoyDashboardRide.joyrideStepsModelPhase2: <span> Makhalidwe (kapena SubConditions) amagwiritsidwa ntchito kusonyeza kugwirizanitsa kapena kusokoneza zikhulupiliro pakati pa mmodzi kapena angapo okondana nawo. Dinani kuwonjezera chithunzi kuti mutsegule Pulojekiti Yamagulu, kwezani ndi kuponyera zigawo zofunikira pa (dontho lachigawo) bokosi la zokambirana ndikufotokoze ngati Chikhalidwechi chiyenera kukhala Chogwira Ntchito kapena Chosachita. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.ClickO: Zithunzi zimalongosolezedwa ndipo zimagwiritsidwa ntchito pogwiritsa ntchito Knowledge Base. Dinani pa {photo1} kuti muwonjezere zinthu ndi {photo2} kuti muwonjezere maumboni. Ingolani mwachidule PubMed Identifier (PMID) kuti mupange mawonekedwe osakaniza ndikugwirizanitsa ziganizo. Malingaliro angayikidwe molingana ndi kufalitsa ndi mtundu wa deta. Dinani mwachidule pazokambirana ndipo sankhani chizindikiro chimene mukufuna kuwonjezera.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Collab: Kugwirizanitsa ndichinthu chofunikira pa zopezeka zatsopano pogwiritsira ntchito kayendedwe kake - ndipo ziri pamtima pa Gulu Lonse! Kusindikiza pa {photo} kukutengerani ku tsamba la Gawo, kukuthandizani kuti muwonjezere othandizira, pangani zolumikizana zogawanika ndi kufalitsa zofufuza.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Select: <span> Sankhani zomwe mukufuna kuti mutenge. Kulimbana ndi bokosi kamodzi ndikutayika kwa ntchito (kutchulidwa ndi chizindikiro chofiira), ndipo kudindira bokosi kawiri ndi kusintha kwapindunji (kotchulidwa ndi greenmark). Kuwombera kupitilira kachiwiri kumachotsa kusintha. Zosintha zingayambidwe musanayambe kapena mukuyimira kuti muwonetsere kusintha kwa mphamvu mu nthawi yeniyeni. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase2.C: Dinani {photo} kuti mupange dziko loyamba. Nthaŵi yoyamba idalengedwa, chizindikirocho chikuwonetsedwa mkati mwa gulu la Internal Components. Kuchokera m'ndandanda iyi, sankhani zigawo zomwe mumafuna kugwira ntchito pachiyambi cha zofanana (t = 0).

Dinani {photo} kuti mulembe kuthamanga kwayimodzi. Chithunzicho chidzakhala chobiriwira pamene zojambula zikuchitika. Zosintha pazoyesera kapena kusintha kwasintha, ndi nthawi yawo yolemba nthawi, zolembedwa ndi zosungidwa mkati mwa kuyimilira, kuyesetsanso kuyesetseratu kuyesayesa.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Mul: <span> Zowonjezera zowonjezera zingasankhidwe pogwiritsa ntchito makalata ochezera. Mutasankhidwa, mukhoza kuchotsa, kukopera, kapena kuyambiranso kuyesa panthaŵi imodzimodziyo. Izi ndi zothandiza makamaka pakukonzekera mayesero mutatha kusintha kusintha kwa chitsanzo cha chitsanzo. </ span>,
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Col: Dinani {photo} pafupi ndi Mtsinje Wokongola: chizindikiro kuti mupange kuthamanga kwayimira. Kufufuza kusinthasintha kotheka sikungathe kulembedwa, choncho, zochitika zakunja (zomwe zikutanthauza) kapena kusintha kwake, ndipo zochitika zawo (zomwe zimatchulidwa nthawi) zimayenera kutsogozedwa kale. Werengani phunziro la Simulation Flows kuti mudziwe zambiri.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Onc: <span> Mukadakhala ndi graph yomwe ilipo pano mukhoza kukopera Activity Relations Graph ngati fayilo ya PNG podutsa pano. </ span>
